---
import { HERO_IMAGE, SITE } from '../lib/site';
---

<header class="relative min-h-[100svh] flex flex-col justify-end overflow-hidden pt-16 sm:pt-[4.25rem]">
  <div class="absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true">
    <img
      src={HERO_IMAGE}
      alt=""
      width="1920"
      height="1080"
      class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover object-center scale-105 animate-fade-in"
      fetchpriority="high"
      decoding="async"
    />
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-ink via-ink/55 to-ink/20"
    ></div>
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,transparent_30%,rgb(7_8_12/0.35)_100%)]"
    ></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto w-full max-w-screen-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-14 sm:pb-20 pt-24">
    <p class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tighter animate-fade-up">
      selfdriving<span class="text-ember">.monster</span>
    </p>

    <h1
      class="mt-4 max-w-4xl text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-display font-bold tracking-tighter leading-[0.95] animate-fade-up delay-1"
    >
      The machines are already driving.
      <span class="monster-gradient block mt-1">When do we stop?</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-5 max-w-xl text-base sm:text-lg text-zinc-300/95 animate-fade-up delay-2">
      A clear-eyed, data-backed guide to self-driving vehicles — Tesla FSD, Cybercab, Waymo, and why
      industry leads the autonomy race. Data as of {SITE.dataAsOf}.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 animate-fade-up delay-3">
      <a
        href="#tesla"
        class="inline-flex min-h-12 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-2xl bg-white px-6 sm:px-8 text-ink font-semibold text-sm sm:text-base hover:bg-zinc-100 active:scale-[0.985] transition shadow-xl shadow-black/40"
      >
        Explore Tesla’s progress
        <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="#acquire"
        class="inline-flex min-h-12 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-white/25 bg-white/5 px-6 sm:px-7 font-semibold text-sm sm:text-base hover:bg-white/10 transition backdrop-blur-sm"
      >
        Acquire this domain
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
